data.description: Pride of ownership welcomes you into this charming Southeast Aurora Townhome located within the Cherry Creek School District.  Recent updates in the past year include the updated kitchen, bathroom, flooring, new appliances and fresh paint. An extra feature along with the 3 bed 2 bath home includes a bonus room ready for your own personal use such as a home office, nursery, home gym, art/sewing room or wherever your imagination takes you. In addition to the exquisite updates throughout, the home is conveniently located near an abundance of major shopping, local restaurants, trails, hiking and community recreational center.  Easy access to E-470, I-25, 225 and DIA. Move in, unpack and enjoy your new home.
